<div class="grid_11 text alpha">
    <h2 class="colophon">Development and Maintenance</h2>
    <div class="grid_6 text alpha">
    	<h3>Web Application Platform</h3>
        <p>Team Member: <strong>Manu Smith</strong></p>
    	<ul>
    		<li>PHP architecture built with <strong><a href="http://framework.zend.com/">Zend Framework</a></strong>.</li>
    		<li>JavaScript framework and tools by <strong><a href="http://prototypejs.org/">Prototype</a></strong>.</li>
    		<li>Revision control is managed through <strong><a href="http://subversion.tigris.org/">Subversion</a></strong>.</li>
    		<li>The web MVC is custom built using <strong><a href="http://www.smarty.net/">Smarty template engine</a></strong>.</li>
    		<li>Geolocation functionality is provided through <strong><a href="http://code.google.com/apis/maps/">Google Maps</a></strong>.</li>
    	</ul>
    </div>
    <div class="grid_5 text omega">
    	<h3>Web User Interface</h3>
        <p>Team Member: <strong>Alex Burr</strong></p>
